Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.40,1:13:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,rhythm. They stayed like that
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.06,1:13:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.23,1:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,long minutes. The shaft still
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.84,1:13:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,half erect inside her. Their
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.36,1:13:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,bodies entangled in a
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.25,1:13:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,traced light patterns with his
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.87,1:13:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,fingertips along her spine,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.33,1:14:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,descending to the curve of her
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.95,1:14:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,buttocks. While she stroked the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.68,1:14:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,hair at the nape of his neck,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.29,1:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling the goosebumps under her
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.07,1:14:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,touch. The room seemed smaller,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.33,1:14:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,more intimate, wrapped in the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.45,1:14:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,smell of skin, satisfied desire
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.71,1:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.93,1:14:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,something deeper that reaffirmed
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.63,1:14:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,itself with each beat of the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.13,1:14:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,heart. Little by little the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.56,1:14:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,movement
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.99,1:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,slowed to lazy touches. Soft
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.77,1:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,kisses on shoulders and chins.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.67,1:14:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Glances that said everything
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.45,1:14:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.23,1:14:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,begun with the recognition in
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.89,1:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the kiss, now sealed itself in
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.61,1:14:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the post-pleasure stillness,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.69,1:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,where each shared breath
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.89,1:14:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,reinforced the certainty that
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.35,1:14:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,this time, they wouldn't lose
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.80,1:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,each other again.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.05,1:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They stayed there. Their
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.33,1:14:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing took time to steady.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.93,1:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't pull away right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.07,1:14:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She ran her fingers through his
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.64,1:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,hair. He rested his forehead on
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.22,1:14:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.89,1:14:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to do this
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.48,1:14:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,right, he said, to love without
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.32,1:14:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,holding on. I don't know how
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.97,1:14:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.21,1:14:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then we learn together. Little
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.06,1:14:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by little, she said. He nodded
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.90,1:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,against her forehead and stayed
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.81,1:15:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there. A silent seal, with no
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.85,1:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,word over top of it. In the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.75,1:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,following weeks, Kitt gradually
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.94,1:15:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,settled
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.43,1:15:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,into his old room at the Quint
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.16,1:15:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mansion, Houdora, who had always
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.00,1:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,known how to receive my
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.33,1:15:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,questies and senators with
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.88,1:15:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,equally calibrated coldness,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.55,1:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't know how to receive a sun
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.45,1:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.05,1:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She learned at breakfast,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.44,1:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,without a manual. She sat on the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.23,1:15:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,other side of the table and
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.74,1:15:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,served
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.07,1:15:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,jam without asking. The way Kitt
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.33,1:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,had liked it when he was 14.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.32,1:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitt let her. The silences hurt
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.51,1:15:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,less each day. Marlo adopted
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.15,1:15:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitt at the first lunch where
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.84,1:15:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,she was introduced to him. She
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.60,1:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,called
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.95,1:15:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,him borrowed brother. And the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.50,1:15:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,next day she was already sending
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.22,1:15:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,jokes by note to his room.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.03,1:15:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas appointed himself a
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.50,1:15:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,official godfather of no more
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.20,1:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,dropping the ball. An expression
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.07,1:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,he
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.19,1:15:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,repeated with the face of a
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.82,1:15:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,serious lawyer every time Jago
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.62,1:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,hesitated before any decision
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.37,1:15:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,involving
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.91,1:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Roenah. Roenah accepted the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.60,1:15:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,offer from the intercepted
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.23,1:15:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,letter, with the terms
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.61,1:15:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,rearranged by herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.35,1:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She wrote the first report in 15
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.33,1:16:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,days, then another. Then a
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.94,1:16:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,third, that Hollis Vaughan read
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.86,1:16:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,from
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.11,1:16:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,a far and didn't comment on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.99,1:16:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Automize, the wedding was on an
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.06,1:16:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,autumn afternoon. In a garden of
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.21,1:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,old
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.41,1:16:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,trees and moss hanging from the
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.26,1:16:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,branches far from any hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.88,1:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no society
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.07,1:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,photographer,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.85,1:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,no published list, no orchestra.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.04,1:16:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a string quartet that
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.16,1:16:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,played softly enough
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.53,1:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to let the birds keep singing
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.12,1:16:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,over it. Kneeve held the bouquet
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.87,1:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,before the ceremony with a
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.30,1:16:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,reverence
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.79,1:16:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,no one asked for. She cried
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.54,1:16:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,without hiding it when she
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.22,1:16:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,handed it over. Roenah kissed
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.10,1:16:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,her cheek.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.25,1:16:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitt stood to the groom's left,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.99,1:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in a charcoal gray suit that
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.56,1:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas had helped choose. The
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.14,1:16:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,scar on
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.53,1:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,his eyebrow had softened over
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.98,1:16:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the last months. He looked at
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.44,1:16:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,his brother when Roenah began to
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.04,1:16:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,walk,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.29,1:16:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jago looked back, and for a
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.28,1:16:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,few seconds that Holl garden fit
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.33,1:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,into a single frame.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.15,1:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd or a cried without hiding
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.94,1:16:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it, seated in the first row,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.55,1:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,with a handkerchief she never
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.22,1:16:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,got
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.39,1:16:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,around to using. Besides her,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.01,1:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the chair that months earlier
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.62,1:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,would have stayed empty was
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.12,1:16:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,occupied
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.57,1:17:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,by Kitt, who had settled in next
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.40,1:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to his mother between the
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.83,1:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ceremony and the toast. No one
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.54,1:17:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,explained.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.69,1:17:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no need. Marlo gave a
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.74,1:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,short, sharp speech. She began
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.72,1:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,by saying she'd be brief
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.30,1:17:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.83,1:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,long love puts you to sleep and
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.59,1:17:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,drew a laugh even from Udora.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.23,1:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked at Roenah and said,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.37,1:17:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you were the best journalist in
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.07,1:17:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,this city when I met you. You
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.65,1:17:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,still are. Only now you right by
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.41,1:17:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,choice,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.09,1:17:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,not by fright. And that's the
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.46,1:17:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,only thing I've wanted for you
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.88,1:17:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,since the very first pre-dorn we
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.39,1:17:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,answered the phone crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.06,1:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Roenah laughed with a runny
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.80,1:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,nose. Jago squeezed her hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.66,1:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Silas raised his
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.69,1:17:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,glass a little later, and
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.21,1:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,mentioned in passing that a
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.86,1:17:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,certain airis had gotten engaged
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.81,1:17:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.93,1:17:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.81,1:17:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,one, and also in passing, poor
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.85,1:17:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,banker. They laughed. A telegram
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.03,1:17:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived by Fielens' hand,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.21,1:17:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Roenah recognized the
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.35,1:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,handwriting even before reading
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.02,1:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it. Paulis Vaughan had sent
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.48,1:17:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,forwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.59,1:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck in there. She tucked
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.09,1:17:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the folded paper into the pocket
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.70,1:17:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of her dress. There were things
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.25,1:17:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that got resolved without a big
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.87,1:18:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,letter. Only with a dry line
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.34,1:18:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,from someone who once asked for
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.96,1:18:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,more
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.17,1:18:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,than they had a right to, Dyson,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.76,1:18:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the following winter came softly
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.36,1:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to the house near the river.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.75,1:18:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That morning had a pale, clean
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.85,1:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,light with no wind. Roenah was
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.94,1:18:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in the kitchen in a robe,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.97,1:18:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,her pinned up hair loose. Jago
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.76,1:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,came down in his socks, with the
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.66,1:18:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,face of someone who'd woken up
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.45,1:18:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,happy and didn't quite know why
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.26,1:18:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,yet. She took his hand before he
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.14,1:18:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,could take his coffee. She
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.66,1:18:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,carried
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.07,1:18:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it to her own belly. She kept
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.95,1:18:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at him. Jago took a full
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.01,1:18:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,second to understand. When he
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.89,1:18:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,understood, his eyes filled and
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.72,1:18:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't overflow. He rested his
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.50,1:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,forehead on hers without
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.92,1:18:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.45,1:18:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The hand that was over her belly
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.32,1:18:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed there quiet. The same way
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.19,1:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it had lain flat on her back
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.83,1:18:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.59,1:18:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when, he asked quietly,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.48,1:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,almost into her mouth. It's
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.25,1:18:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,still early,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.21,1:18:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Roenah said, but it is. He
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.86,1:18:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,breathed in deep. He laughed
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.64,1:18:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,without sound. He stayed there
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.55,1:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with his forehead
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.63,1:18:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,pressed to hers for a long time
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.26,1:18:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,without needing to say anything
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.90,1:18:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,big. On the other side of the
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.43,1:18:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.35,1:19:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the living room opened in
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.65,1:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,silence toward the river. Roenah
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.33,1:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,looked over his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.63,1:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Near the window, in the chair
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.20,1:19:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that for months had stayed empty
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.93,1:19:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,without anyone explaining,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.05,1:19:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,someone was sitting. Kitt was
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.76,1:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,reading the newspaper with a
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.42,1:19:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,steaming mug beside him. His
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.07,1:19:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,hair
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.31,1:19:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,still wet from the shower. His
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.34,1:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,feet resting on the stool. He
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.30,1:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,felt her gaze, looked up, smiled
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.47,1:19:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with just one corner of his
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.24,1:19:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth. He went back to the
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.95,1:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,newspaper. Jago looked too. He
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.92,1:19:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed there
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.71,1:19:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a second. He squeezed Roenah's
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.89,1:19:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,hand more firmly over their own
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.14,1:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,child. The winter light crossed
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.39,1:19:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the
